How could anybody ask for the "recipe" with a straight face? This is, as a previous poster correctly noted, oil and lemon juice on a few veggies. A bit of balsamic, some "parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme" with avocado, tomato and zucchini and you have - well, a whole other recipe! Indeed, why didn't the geniuses at Epicurious suggest all these additions?

