The "recipe" is basically olive oil and lemon dressing that you pour over pasta and veggies. I tried it and found it unbelievably boring. Since the loophole is in the description - that it lends itself to other vegetables, I did the following: I used tomatoes, avocado and zucchini as my veggies and added basil. I also added a splash of balsamic vinegar. So I guess it's a whole other recipe, huh? ;-)

